:false,"disclosed_at":"2019-07-06T17:59:06.463Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2019-06-06T17:58:56.753Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Manipulating an order request JSON object, containing an additional item with a negative quantity directly manipulates the total amount of the order.\n\nIn the following JSON request, an order is submitted for 2 ChickenBurgers ($12 each), as well as -1 BreadPuddings ($9 each).\n\nThe total price after tax calculates as $18.70 and is accepted by the system. The attached screenshots show the previous orders, indicating that only $18.70 was charged for the transaction.\n\n```json\n{\"card_uuid\": \"09ef096d-18d7-4cb4-83b7-5bd15d310aac\", \"city\": \"Cambridge\", \"email\": \"mthompson@hexwave.com\", \"first_name\": \"Matt\", \"last_name\": \"Thompson\", \"line1\": \"1230 Massachusetts Ave\", \"order\": {\"charges\": {\"items\": [{\"item_id\": \"254baa85-92c1-412e-a391-aaf44508d882\", \"name\": \"ChickenBurger\", \"price\": 1200, \"quantity\": 2, \"instructions\": \"\", \"total\": 1200, \"modifiers\": [], \"sides\": []}, {\"item_id\": \"9169bfc1-2ee1-455b-ad65-aeadd36f46eb\", \"name\": \"BreadPudding\", \"price\": 900, \"quantity\": -1, \"instructions\": \"\", \"total\": 900, \"modifiers\": [], \"sides\": []}], \"taxes\": 290, \"tip\": {\"amount\": 0}, \"total\": 1870}, \"confirmation_code\": \"upserve-hacker-cafe-32870\", \"fulfillment_info\": {\"customer\": {\"email\": \"mthompson@hexwave.com\", \"first_name\": \"Matt\", \"last_name\": \"Thompson\", \"phone\": \"555-555-5555\"}, \"delivery_info\": {\"address\": {\"address_line1\": \"1230 Massachusetts Ave\", \"address_line2\": null, \"city\": \"Cambridge\", \"country\": \"\", \"state\": \"MA\", \"zip_code\": \"02138\"}}, \"instructions\": \"\", \"type\": \"delivery\"}, \"id\": \"a168f311-f0bf-416c-b813-b277e3a7b5b3\", \"payments\": {\"payments\": [{\"amount\": 0, \"payment_type\": \"CREDIT\", \"tip_amount\": 0}], \"total\": 3190}, \"time_placed\": \"2018-06-11T20:48:51.313Z\"}, \"order_total\": 3190, \"phone_number\": \"555-555-5555\", \"state\": \"MA\", \"store_pretty_url\": \"upserve-lounge-test-providence-2\", \"submission_id\": \"a168f311-f0bf-416c-b813-b277e3a7b5b3\", \"text_alerts\": false, \"zip\": \"02138\"}\n```\n\n## Impact\n\nThe attacker can reduce the price of the order.","weakness":{"id":65,"name":"Business Logic Errors"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":307763,"file_name":"Screen_Shot_2018-06-11_at_2.36.37_PM.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/307/763/442989a263819ed500aa8c425f830a0034232710/Screen_Shot_2018-06-11_at_2.36.37_PM.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screen_Shot_2018-06-11_at_2.36.37_PM.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screen_Shot_2018-06-11_at_2.36.37_PM.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYJPM5INV%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T092917Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIGPTFP%2F%2B61NRXKxUCRRiOEw%2FyEXMoJI30jSWgewoYzlYAiATW70r0%2Ft4BCmx%2BIRRvI9N9Vm6tq25cJqmqyf8P9oJnSq6BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMlnlVa%2Fn%2F5%2FBwcq%2BdKo4F1YnOHtgpcuOI6MB5pFrZ1JRxajUzrmu66Bs%2BaH059f9y01fPv%2FrjUZqEro3Jo9934IhhUwQj4gQeQ52XFU4tL%2Fl7ANAcg%2BweyQf%2FlO3JCodLg6QOdgOquP7BbCsXjast8Pomf8KP1lmk7IIMD7J9DS4cjH6SQasi3CttqywzFCaRrB8cbzZNYwGpMcshlGieMrYvXOKXlnFS%2Bvyupk%2BdoPGms%2F3cgeV%2BcDw50A71YHut794drWOwB%2BEgOIDnJqc%2FodmOUDjNrGX2PYH98D58CQI6kF0KLfi9CZmpJrhPYWDkdXTTag4OHihpyrvYSsSmxgEN1mpxlQWp3qqjt9qoTl0ks45f5BDGWqJfXqS6BToA%2FyYcov9sqsrq4OPo9luLGlSC2n3bSDp7b0kZjA1KI8sleyE39CFdrHoEX%2B7oWvUWQgHphH3Q8BMmkSeejy70EmY5sY8nHxzxh7Dad05tIOqTFbZ%2BZgtuZT5FDbkFzkwFhf31nqsw52N8uaKjg5OC9z